Package au.edu.tafesa.spsbuddyrestservice.model

Interface User

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, org.springframework.security.core.userdetails.UserDetails
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    UserImpl
    public interface User
extends org.springframework.security.core.userdetails.UserDetails
    User interface describes class that provides core app user's information. User can have only one role in the app.
